
Todays Soft Skill Tip:

Day 14 – Feedback: The Shortcut to Growth

Most people avoid feedback; achievers invite it. Constructive Feedback isn’t failure — it’s a mirror that helps you grow faster.

Each time you listen to feedback without defending yourself, you gain an edge most ignore.

Feedback accepted is improvement unlocked.

Task:
Ask one person today — “What’s one thing I can improve in my communication or confidence?”

Listen fully. Don’t justify — just note and reflect.

